beer.beer_name: Red Right Hand DDH Red IPA
beer.beer_description:
440ml Cans - Limited Release

You'll see him in your nightmares, you'll see him in your dreams. He'll appear out of nowhere but he ain't what he seems.

Red Right Hand is a good beer with bad intentions.

A decadent, full bodied Red Ale with lashings of biscuit and burnt sugar malt flavours. Massive blasts of hop aromas from Chinook, Amarillo and Simcoe. Mouth coating sensory overload of pine, spicy and citrus hop flavours with a long bitter finish.

At 7.8% ABV Red Right Hand is ready to take your tastebuds on a wild ride…

Are you ready?
